site_description: Unimarc is a Chilean family supermarket chain.
title: Unimarc
description: In April 2021, the Chilean supermarket chain Unimarc was allegedly breached. The stolen data contains email addresses and additional personal information. This breach is being privately shared on the internet.

site_description: This is the official website of Diponegoro University, a public university in Semarang, Central Java, Indonesia.
title: Universitas Diponegoro
description: At an unconfirmed date, the Indonesian university Universitas Diponegoro was allegedly breached. The stolen data contains full names, dates of birth, addresses, phone numbers, religions, email addresses and additional personal information. This breach is being privately shared on the internet.
